// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <cast exp> => Exp
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <exp1> => Exp
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <inst var decl> => Decl
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <program> => Program
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  <unary exp> => Exp
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 7: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ `}
// 8: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 9: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `}
// 10: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ `}
// 11: <type> ::= `int
// 12: <type> ::= `boolean
// 13: <type> ::= `void
// 14: <type> ::= `null
// 15: <type> ::= ID
// 16: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 17: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 18: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 19: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 20: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 21: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 22: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 23: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 24: <stmt> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 25: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 26: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 27: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 28: <exp> ::= <exp4>
// 29: <exp4> ::= `true
// 30: <exp4> ::= `false
// 31: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `+ <exp3>
// 32: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `- <exp2>
// 33: <exp4> ::= <exp3>
// 34: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `* <exp2>
// 35: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `/ <exp2>
// 36: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `% <exp2>
// 37: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `&& <exp2>
// 38: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `< <exp2>
// 39: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `> <exp2>
// 40: <exp3> ::= <exp2>
// 41: <exp2> ::= <cast exp>
// 42: <exp2> ::= <unary exp>
// 43: <cast exp> ::= `( <type> `) <cast exp>
// 44: <cast exp> ::= `( <type> `) <exp1>
// 45: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `instanceof <type>
// 46: <unary exp> ::= `+ <unary exp>
// 47: <unary exp> ::= `- <unary exp>
// 48: <unary exp> ::= `! <unary exp>
// 49: <unary exp> ::= <exp1>
// 50: <exp1> ::= ID
// 51: <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 52: <exp1> ::= INTLIT
// 53: <exp1> ::= STRINGLIT
// 54: <exp1> ::= CHARLIT
// 55: <exp1> ::= `this
// 56: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 57: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 58: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 59: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 60: any ::= {0..127}
// 61: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 62: ws ::= " "
// 63: ws ::= {10}
// 64: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 65: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 66: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 67: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 68: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x" ws*
// 69: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x"
// 70: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 71: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 72: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 73: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 74: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 75: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 76: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 77: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 78: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 79: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 80: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 81: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 82: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 83: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 84: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 85: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 86: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 87: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 88: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 89: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 90: `instanceof ::= "#" "i" "n" ws*
// 91: `instanceof ::= "#" "i" "n"
// 92: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 93: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 94: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 95: `! ::= "!"
// 96: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 97: `% ::= "%"
// 98: `&& ::= "@" "&" ws*
// 99: `&& ::= "@" "&"
// 100: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 101: `* ::= "*"
// 102: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 103: `( ::= "("
// 104: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 105: `) ::= ")"
// 106: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 107: `{ ::= "{"
// 108: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 109: `} ::= "}"
// 110: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 111: `- ::= "-"
// 112: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 113: `+ ::= "+"
// 114: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 115: `= ::= "="
// 116: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 117: `[ ::= "["
// 118: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 119: `] ::= "]"
// 120: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 121: `< ::= "<"
// 122: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 123: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 124: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 125: `; ::= ";"
// 126: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 127: `/ ::= "/"
// 128: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 129: ID ::= letter128
// 130: ID ::= letter idChar* $$0
// 131: ID ::= letter $$0
// 132: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$1
// 133: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$1
// 134: INTLIT ::= digit128 ws*
// 135: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 136: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$2
// 137: INTLIT ::= "0" $$2
// 138: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 139: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 140: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$3
// 141: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$3
// 142: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 143: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 144: idChar ::= letter
// 145: idChar ::= digit
// 146: idChar ::= "_"
// 147: idChar128 ::= letter128
// 148: idChar128 ::= digit128
// 149: idChar128 ::= {223}
// 150: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 151: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 152: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 153: digit* ::= digit
// 154: any* ::= any* any
// 155: any* ::= any
// 156: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 157: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 158: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit
// 159: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit
// 160: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 161: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 162: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 163: idChar* ::= idChar
// 164: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>
// 165: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <class decl>
// 166: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 167: ws* ::= ws
// 168: $$0 ::= idChar128 ws*
// 169: $$0 ::= idChar128
// 170: $$1 ::= digit128 ws*
// 171: $$1 ::= digit128
// 172: $$2 ::= hexDigit128 ws*
// 173: $$2 ::= hexDigit128
// 174: $$3 ::= any128 ws*
// 175: $$3 ::= any128
// =================symbols=======================
// 0: $$start
// 1: <start>
// 2: ws*

// 4: <class decl>+
// 5: <class decl>
// 6: `class
// 7: ID

// 11: `extends

// 20: `int

// 24: `[

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 47
        "#" => shift: 106
        ws => shift: 99
        <program> => shift: 164
        `class => shift: 350
        <start> => shift: 373
        ws* => shift: 213
        {10} => shift: 25
        " " => shift: 60
        <class decl> => shift: 363

**** STATE 2 ****
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `[

    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%
    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `&&

    ws ::= {10} [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `*

**** STATE 3 ****
    `] ::= "]" ws* <%> // $NT
    `] ::= "]" ws* <%> // <empty bracket pair>
    `] ::= "]" ws* <%> // ID

**** STATE 190 ****
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 !<empty bracket pair> <%!<empty bracket pair>> // `[
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // <empty bracket pair>
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // ID
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // `%
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // `&&
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // `)
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // `*
    ID ::= letter [idChar*] $$0 <%> // `+

    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> [#] `else <stmt> // `}
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `while `( <exp> `) <stmt> // <stmt>
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `while `( <exp> `) <stmt> // `}

    <type> ::= [#] <%> <type> <empty bracket pair> // <empty bracket pair>

**** STATE 213 ****
    <start> ::= ws* <%> <program> // $
    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // ws
    -----------------------

    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>

    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // `}
    <decl in class>* ::= <%> <decl in class>* <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= <%> <decl in class>* <decl in class> // `}
    <decl in class>* ::= [<decl in class>*] <%> <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= [<decl in class>*] <%> <decl in class> // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ [<stmt>*] `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID `( `) `{ [<stmt>*] `} // `}

    `public ::= <%> "#" "p" "u" ws* // `void
    `} ::= <%> "}" [ws*] // $
    `} ::= <%> "}" [ws*] // <class decl>
    `} ::= <%> "}" ws* // $
    `} ::= <%> "}" ws* // <class decl>

    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `]

**** STATE 323 ****
    ID ::= letter128 ws* !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `[
    ID ::= letter128 ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> // ID

    ws* ::= ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> ws // `]
    ws* ::= ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> ws // `instanceof
